{"type": "article", "id": 44365, "title": "想玩镭射雕刻？有这个小盒子就够了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-22T23:07:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43427, "name": "与熊设计"}, {"id": 43428, "name": "Ideoxo"}, {"id": 36875, "name": "DesignLibero"}, {"id": 43429, "name": "Muherz"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 189, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170822180748Wix7GTnUzJvECLdw.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Cubiio by Muherz</h3><p>你有没有想过有一天能在家就能动手完成一次安全的镭射雕刻？最近，台湾初创公司 Muherz 带来了这款名为 Cubiio 的镭射雕刻机，成功将原本身材庞大的机械设备缩小到了掌上方块的大小。这个小方块与配套的手机应用通过蓝牙相连，只要选取好图案就能将其雕刻在物品上。为了保护双眼，Muherz 还设计了专用的保护壳和护目镜。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/880456201/cubiio-the-most-compact-laser-engraver\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 379 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708221807560hj1pbrXW2qK4gkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180755eSVzawCGc1uTWj3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.514815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180756gHocESuZKU8MbNhF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560494\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180755HhvTBJOudFUxpYqV.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.502469\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708221807552NlPV8sUK6ZLMqy0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734568\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>分x水泥袋纸 by Ideoxo</h3><p>在不支持移动支付的商店或是去海外旅行时，为了不影响身后的客人，难免会出现手拿一堆找零措手不及的情况。为了减轻购物时的烦恼，台湾设计品牌“与熊设计”（<a href=\"http://www.ideoso.com.tw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ideoxo</a>）推出了一系列只要轻轻一甩就能自动将纸币和零钱分离的分钱包。最近，他们又在帆布、单宁布的基础上，加入了由水泥袋制成的款式。由于水泥袋采用牛皮纸和织带组成，具有耐重、防泼水的特性，而材质本身又相当轻盈。你可以通过<a href=\"http://ideoxo.com.tw/portal_c1_cnt.php?owner_num=c1_133547&amp;button_num=c1&amp;folder_id=&amp;website_language_id=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从新台币 1360 元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180517qDHj9w5athxNOG3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180517o18Y5TvDem9sfkRP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180517Awi7mb2juZQvN1EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180517XhbnJ0BGQF5rL2fj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Patchwork by Giulia Pesce &amp; Ruggero Bastita</h3><p>在难民接待中心或是灾害过后聚集了大量人群的公共居住空间，该如何确保人们的隐私和舒适度？针对近年来欧洲的难民潮，丹麦科灵设计学院（Designskolen Kolding）工业设计系的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/giuliaandruggero\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giulia Pesce 和 Ruggero Bastita</a> 借鉴寝室布局，设计了这套名为 Patchwork 的模块化家具。他们的灵感来源于拜访意大利难民接待中心时的所见所闻：面对相似度极高的家具，那些无家可归的人们都在试图用私人物品让自己寄居的小空间变得更具个性化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180535DCwYfhJprTu7Z8yb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180535sjcdLhGrTXPxV1R8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180535GoBflJpWvzhAg4jR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708221805369YPhsr63xynBwQJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180536HPYasW1xqp4lJUQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Supertaster 2.0 by Lena Beigel</h3><p>在一道佳肴还未入口前，我们就已经为摆盘所影响，在心中暗暗为它们打分了。由德国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.lenabeigel.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lena Beigel</a> 带来的 Supertaster 2.0，是她在同名毕设作品的基础上改良而成的三角形食器。配合六边形或是长方形的木制底座，食物设计师既可以简单地用高低不平的餐盘填满，也可以将它们像积木那样留白或是堆叠起来，营造出新奇的用餐体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180547bUefRcMJonPIp6wK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180547M7XZEzCBUfu2ROVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180547sizgED30WqjJbpQB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708221805480ujEq8dG3OyP29Qs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713580\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180548Uk84AqtZPp6oGOwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Leaf by DesignLibero</h3><p>带汪星人出门，如何才能确保它们安全、方便地饮水呢？最近，意大利设计工作室 DesignLibero 受宠物用品品牌 <a href=\"https://www.unitedpets.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">United Pets</a> 的委托，设计了这个名为 Leaf 的便携式水碗。它的造型正如其名，就像是一张柔软的树叶，只要安装在灌满水的矿泉水瓶口，稍许倾斜就能让宠物解渴了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180601C6nu8iKWesNlQH02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180600hvrQ8xYefOGl9Cj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180600xXnB7lRNJuIaUApy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180600XA716Yjf4pBnRLxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nature Insects by Raku Inoue</h3><p>写实的昆虫图鉴让人心生恐惧？身为昆虫爱好者，加拿大日裔设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/rakuinoue\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raku Inoue</a> 决定用一种更容易被接受的方式改变人们对昆虫的偏见。为此，他在白纸上布置简单的花朵和绿植，还原出天牛、瓢虫和黑寡妇等昆虫的形态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180619yuBeGbgsOJMAzHYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180619SO13j4FqJ2t6Xuho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180619tdbDSoJ7kirFHNLc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180620Anu0zlyfah1tIgeb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170822180620BsDdKEx1VUcGwvZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}